COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 76, L.D. 140
1 Initiative: Provides funding for increased homestead property tax exemption
2 reimbursement to municipalities starting with the property tax year beginning April 1,
3 2026.
4 GENERAL FUND 2025-26 2026-27
5 All Other $0 $14,025,000
6 __________ __________
7 GENERAL FUND TOTAL $0 $14,025,000
