9 ADMINISTRATIVE AND FINANCIAL
10 SERVICES, DEPARTMENT OF
11 DEPARTMENT TOTALS 2025-26 2026-27
12
13 GENERAL FUND $47,640 $14,025,000
14 __________ __________
15 DEPARTMENT TOTAL - ALL FUNDS $47,640 $14,025,000
169 '
17 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
18 number to read consecutively.
19 SUMMARY
2200 This amendment reduces future increases of the homestead property tax exemption to
2211 $5,000 per year beginning in 2026 and caps the exemption increases at $50,000 of the just
2222 value of the homestead. The amendment also provides that once the exemption amount
2233 reaches $50,000 in 2032, the amount of the exemption will be adjusted for inflation
2244 annually. The amendment also adds an appropriations and allocations section.
2255 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
2266 (See attached)
