19 SUMMARY
2200 This amendment reduces future increases of the homestead property tax exemption to
2211 $5,000 per year beginning in 2026 and caps the exemption increases at $50,000 of the just
2222 value of the homestead. The amendment also provides that once the exemption amount
2233 reaches $50,000 in 2032, the amount of the exemption will be adjusted for inflation
